    • upload

      public CompletableFuture<PlotUploader.PlotUploadResult> upload(@NonNull Plot plot)
      Upload a plot and retrieve a result. The plot will be saved into a temporary schematic file and uploaded to the REST service specified by Settings.Arkitektonika.BACKEND_URL.
      Parameters:
      plot - The plot to upload
      Returns:
      a CompletableFuture that provides a PlotUploader.PlotUploadResult if finished.
